




課程大綱










魚類養殖與捕魚之法律問題研究STUDY ON LEGAL PROBLEMS OUT OF THE FISH-BREEDING AND FISHING






開課系所 Department/Institute:  海事所          Ocean Technology and Marine Affairs
開課教師 Instructor:   蔡志方 Tsai, Chih-Fang               
開課學年 Academic Year:   0104
