13.MIDTLYNG, PAUL J. (ed.), PROGRESS IN FISH VACCINOLOGY: THE GRIEG MUSIC HALL CONFERENCE CENTRE, BERGEN, NORWAY APRIL 9-11, 2003: PROCEEDINGS OF THE 3RD INTERNATIONAL SYMPOSIUM ON PROGRESS IN FISH VACCINOLOGY, ORGANISED AND SPONSORED BY THE INTERNATIONAL ASSOCIATION FOR BIOLOGICALS (IABS) AND THE CENTRE FOR VETERINARY CONTRACT RESEARCH AND COMMERCIAL SERVICES, LTD. ( Basel, 2005).
14.PILLAY, T.V.R. AND M.N. KUTTY, AQUACULTURE: PRINCIPLES AND PRACTICES (Blackwell Pub., 2nd ed. 2005).
15.POTACS, M. (HRSG.), KÄRNTNER, JAGD- UND FISCHERREIRECHT(Manzsche Verlag- Und Universitätsbuchhandlung, Wien 2003).    

備註 Remarks
     詳讀魚類養殖與捕撈相關法規




